ios.subtitle: A joint project of OPC & URCNA
Make your beat with one finger

editorialNotes.standard: The next time we have friends over or need extra pep in our workout playlists, were launching this nifty music player. Cue up a song, choose a venue, and LiveTunes amps up the reverb and crowd noise to match. Outdoor Festival is especially heart-thumping and Coffeehouse sounds beautifully stripped down. Plus, swiping up for the on-demand applause never, ever gets old.
